description: The Witch is back! The shocking truth about her children revealed, the Scarlet Witch suffers a nervous breakdown and descends into madness. Manipulated by her father, the mutant terrorist Magneto, Wanda faces her teammates – and her brother, Quicksilver. Can they rescue her from the clutches of Immortus – and save her very sanity? Plus: the return of Iron Man, and the reunion of wartime allies Captain America and the Human Torch. Also featuring the villainy of the Mole Man, Loki, the U-Foes, Master Pandemonium and Hydro-Man! Collecting AVENGERS WEST COAST #51-57 and #60-62.

description:
The attractive Miranda, daughter of Ramos Cordeiro, a land-owning friend of Corico, has been kidnapped by Colonel Fonseca to force her father to betray the Cangaceiros. The Sertão rebels are therefore massacred by government soldiers in the Cordeiro’s Fazenda and Corisco is also killed. But Mister No will not let the death of his friend go unpunished: the “gringo” will have his revenge!

"Tutto Mister No" n. 5 released on October, 1989.
name: La Vendetta del Gringo

description:
Zè Baiano, the Lieutenant of Capitão Corisco, unbeknowns to his leader, provokes his men against the undefended Fazendas. They massacre, hunt and kill. Mister No stops Zè Baiano, but he is more and more undecided: he doesn’t know whether to continue fighting with them or to leave. And betrayal lingers in the air among the Cangaceiros….

"Tutto Mister No" n. 4 released on September, 1989.
name: Morte nel Sertão

description:
Mister No does not know how to choose his clients! The tourists he has carried in his plane to Saint Laurent, in French Guyana, are actually three criminals. They kidnap Julien Remy, an ex convict of Cayenne. They knock Mister No out, as he does not want to cooperate with them, and they get away with Remy along the River Maronì. But, Mister No follows them, together with Remy’s beautiful daughter, Anouk…

"Tutto Mister No" n. 6 released on November, 1989.
name: L’Uomo della Guyana
